etomica.virial

Class ClusterSumMultibody

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.virial.ClusterSum
      • etomica.virial.ClusterSumMultibody
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClusterAbstract, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClusterSumMultibodyShell

    public class ClusterSumMultibody
extends ClusterSum
    Cluster class capable of computing multibody (up to 6th order) contributions to diagrams. Currently, only one type of non-additive Mayer function may be used, although some framework is in place to handle more than one.
